article.headline: Drexel 88, Towson 82
article.story: TOWSON, Md. (AP) -- Tim Whitworth scored a team-high 20 points and grabbed four rebounds to lead Drexel to an 88-82 victory over Towson University Wednesday night. Phil Goss contributed 14 points for Drexel (9-6). Sean Brooks led the team with six rebounds. Mike Green scored a game-high 23 points and a game-high nine rebounds for Towson (6-10).
